#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:4
msgid "MicroPython remote control: mpremote"
msgstr "MicroPython远程控制: mpremote"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:6
msgid ""
"The ``mpremote`` command line tool provides an integrated set of "
"utilities to remotely interact with, manage the filesystem on, and "
"automate a MicroPython device over a serial connection."
msgstr "``mpremote`` 命令行工具提供了一组集成的实用程序，用于通过串行连接与MicroPython设备进行远程交互、管理文件系统和自动化。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:10
msgid "To use mpremote, first install it via ``pip``:"
msgstr "要使用mpremote，首先通过 ``pip`` 安装:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:16
msgid "Or via `pipx <https://pypa.github.io/pipx/>`_:"
msgstr "或通过 `pipx <https://pypa.github.io/pipx/>`_:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:22
msgid ""
"The simplest way to use this tool is just by invoking it without any "
"arguments:"
msgstr "使用这个工具最简单的方法就是不带任何参数地调用它:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:28
msgid ""
"This command automatically detects and connects to the first available "
"USB serial device and provides an interactive terminal that you can use "
"to access the REPL and your program's output.  Serial ports are opened in"
" exclusive mode, so running a second (or third, etc) instance of "
"``mpremote`` will connect to subsequent serial devices, if any are "
"available."
msgstr ""
"该命令自动检测并连接到第一个可用的USB串行设备，并提供一个交互式终端，您可以使用该终端访问REPL和程序的输出。串行端口以独占模式打开，因此运行"
" ``mpremote`` 的第二个(或第三个等) 实例将连接到后续的串行设备，如果有可用的话。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:34
msgid ""
"Additionally ``pipx`` also allows you to directly run ``mpremote`` "
"without installing first:"
msgstr "此外，``pipx`` 还允许您直接运行 ``mpremote`` 而无需先安装:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:42
msgid "Commands"
msgstr "命令"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:44
msgid ""
"``mpremote`` supports being given a series of commands given at the "
"command line which will perform various actions in sequence on a remote "
"MicroPython device. See the :ref:`examples section <mpremote_examples>` "
"below to get an idea of how this works and for some common combinations "
"of commands."
msgstr ""
"``mpremote`` "
"支持在命令行中给出一系列命令，这些命令将在远程MicroPython设备上依次执行各种操作。请参阅下面的:ref:`examples "
"section <mpremote_examples>` ，了解它是如何工作的，以及一些常见的命令组合。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:49
msgid ""
"Each command is of the form ``<command name> [--options] [args...]``. For"
" commands that support multiple arguments (e.g. a list of files), the "
"argument list can be terminated with ``+``."
msgstr ""
"每个命令的形式是 ``<command name> [--options] "
"[args...]``。对于支持多个参数的命令(例如文件列表)，参数列表可以用 ``+`` 结束。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:53
msgid ""
"If no command is specified, the default command is ``repl``. "
"Additionally, if any command needs to access the device, and no earlier "
"``connect`` has been specified, then an implicit ``connect auto`` is "
"added."
msgstr ""
"如果未指定命令，则默认命令为 ``repl``。此外，如果任何命令需要访问设备，并且之前没有指定 ``connect``，则会添加隐式的 "
"``connect auto``。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:57
msgid ""
"In order to get the device into a known state for any action command "
"(except ``repl``), once connected ``mpremote`` will stop any running "
"program and soft-reset the device before running the first command. You "
"can control this behavior using the ``resume`` and ``soft-reset`` "
"commands. See :ref:`auto-connection and auto-soft-reset <mpremote_reset>`"
" for more details."
msgstr ""
"为了使设备进入任何操作命令(除了 ``repl``)的已知状态，一旦连接 ``mpremote`` "
"将停止任何正在运行的程序并在运行第一个命令之前软复位设备。您可以使用 ``resume`` 和 ``soft-reset`` "
"命令控制此行为。参见:ref:`auto-connection and auto-soft-reset <mpremote_reset>` "
"了解更多细节。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:63
msgid "Multiple commands can be specified and they will be run sequentially."
msgstr "可以指定多个命令，它们将依次运行。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:65
msgid "The full list of supported commands are:"
msgstr "支持的命令的完整列表包括："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:67
msgid "`connect <mpremote_command_connect>`"
msgstr "`connect <mpremote_command_connect>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:68
msgid "`disconnect <mpremote_command_disconnect>`"
msgstr "`disconnect <mpremote_command_disconnect>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:69
msgid "`resume <mpremote_command_resume>`"
msgstr "`resume <mpremote_command_resume>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:70
msgid "`soft_reset <mpremote_command_soft_reset>`"
msgstr "`soft_reset <mpremote_command_soft_reset>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:71
msgid "`repl <mpremote_command_repl>`"
msgstr "`repl <mpremote_command_repl>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:72
msgid "`eval <mpremote_command_eval>`"
msgstr "`eval <mpremote_command_eval>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:73
msgid "`exec <mpremote_command_exec>`"
msgstr "`exec <mpremote_command_exec>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:74
msgid "`run <mpremote_command_run>`"
msgstr "`run <mpremote_command_run>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:75
msgid "`fs <mpremote_command_fs>`"
msgstr "`fs <mpremote_command_fs>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:76
msgid "`df <mpremote_command_df>`"
msgstr "`df <mpremote_command_df>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:77
msgid "`edit <mpremote_command_edit>`"
msgstr "`edit <mpremote_command_edit>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:78
msgid "`mip <mpremote_command_mip>`"
msgstr "`mip <mpremote_command_mip>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:79
msgid "`mount <mpremote_command_mount>`"
msgstr "`mount <mpremote_command_mount>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:80
msgid "`unmount <mpremote_command_unmount>`"
msgstr "`unmount <mpremote_command_unmount>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:81
msgid "`romfs <mpremote_command_romfs>`"
msgstr "`romfs <mpremote_command_romfs>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:82
msgid "`rtc <mpremote_command_rtc>`"
msgstr "`rtc <mpremote_command_rtc>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:83
msgid "`sleep <mpremote_command_sleep>`"
msgstr "`sleep <mpremote_command_sleep>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:84
msgid "`reset <mpremote_command_reset>`"
msgstr "`reset <mpremote_command_reset>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:85
msgid "`bootloader <mpremote_command_bootloader>`"
msgstr "`bootloader <mpremote_command_bootloader>`"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:89
msgid "**connect** -- connect to specified device via name:"
msgstr "**connect** -- 通过名称连接到指定设备:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:95
msgid "``<device>`` may be one of:"
msgstr "``<device>`` 可以是以下其中之一:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:97
msgid "``list``: list available devices"
msgstr "``list``: 列表可用设备"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:98
msgid "``auto``: connect to the first available USB serial port"
msgstr "``auto``:连接到第一个可用的USB串行端口"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:99
msgid ""
"``id:<serial>``: connect to the device with USB serial number "
"``<serial>`` (the second column from the ``connect list`` command output)"
msgstr "``id:<serial>``:连接到USB序列号为 ``<serial>`` 的设备(从 ``connect list`` 命令输出的第二列)"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:102
msgid ""
"``port:<path>``: connect to the device with the given path (the first "
"column from the ``connect list`` command output"
msgstr "``port:<path>``:连接到给定路径的设备(从 ``connect list`` 命令输出的第一列)"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:104
msgid ""
"``rfc2217://<host>:<port>``: connect to the device using serial over TCP "
"(e.g. a networked serial port based on RFC2217)"
msgstr "``rfc2217://<host>:<port>``:通过TCP使用串口连接到设备(例如基于rfc2217的网络串口)"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:106
msgid "any valid device name/path, to connect to that device"
msgstr "任何有效的设备名称/路径，以连接到该设备"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:108
msgid ""
"**Note:** Instead of using the ``connect`` command, there are several "
":ref:`pre-defined shortcuts <mpremote_shortcuts>` for common device "
"paths. For example the ``a0`` shortcut command is equivalent to ``connect"
" /dev/ttyACM0`` (Linux), or ``c1`` for ``COM1`` (Windows)."
msgstr ""
"**注意:** 不使用 ``connect`` 命令，有几个 :ref:`pre-defined shortcuts "
"<mpremote_shortcuts>` 用于常见的设备路径。例如， ``a0`` 快捷方式命令相当于 ``connect "
"/dev/ttyACM0`` (Linux)，或 ``c1`` 用于 ``COM1`` (Windows)。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:113
msgid ""
"**Note:** The ``auto`` option will only detect USB serial ports, i.e. a "
"serial port that has an associated USB VID/PID (i.e. CDC/ACM or FTDI-"
"style devices). Other types of serial ports will not be auto-detected."
msgstr ""
"**注:** ``auto`` 选项将只检测USB串行端口，即具有关联USB "
"VID/PID的串行端口(即CDC/ACM或ftdi风格的设备)。其他类型的串行端口将不会被自动检测。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:119
msgid "**disconnect** -- disconnect current device:"
msgstr "**disconnect** -- 断开当前设备："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:125
msgid "After a disconnect, :ref:`auto-soft-reset <mpremote_reset>` is enabled."
msgstr "断开连接后，启用:ref:`auto-soft-reset <mpremote_reset>`。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:129
msgid "**resume** -- maintain existing interpreter state for subsequent commands:"
msgstr "**resume** -- 为后续命令维护现有解释器状态："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:135
msgid ""
"This disables :ref:`auto-soft-reset <mpremote_reset>`. This is useful if "
"you want to run a subsequent command on a board without first soft-"
"resetting it."
msgstr ""
"这会禁用 :ref:`auto-soft-reset "
"<mpremote_reset>`。如果您想在板上运行后续命令，而不首先对其进行软重置，这将非常有用。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:140
msgid "**soft-reset** -- perform a soft-reset of the device:"
msgstr "**软复位**--执行设备的软复位："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:146
msgid ""
"This will clear out the Python heap and restart the interpreter.  It also"
" prevents the subsequent command from triggering :ref:`auto-soft-reset "
"<mpremote_reset>`."
msgstr "这将清除Python堆并重新启动解释器。它还可以防止后续命令触发:ref:`auto-soft-reset <mpremote_reset>`。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:151
msgid "**repl** -- enter the REPL on the connected device:"
msgstr "**repl** -- 在连接的设备上输入REPL："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:157 ../../reference/mpremote.rst:361
msgid "Options are:"
msgstr "选项有："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:159
msgid ""
"``--escape-non-printable``, to print non-printable bytes/characters as "
"their hex code"
msgstr "``--escape-non-printable``，用于将不可打印的字节/字符打印为其十六进制代码"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:160
msgid ""
"``--capture <file>``, to capture output of the REPL session to the given "
"file"
msgstr "``--capture <file>``，捕获到给定文件的REPL会话的输出"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:162
msgid ""
"``--inject-code <string>``, to specify characters to inject at the REPL "
"when ``Ctrl-J`` is pressed. This allows you to automate a common command."
msgstr "``--inject-code <string>``, 指定按 ``Ctrl-J`` 时要在REPL中注入的字符。这允许您自动执行一个常用命令。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:164
msgid ""
"``--inject-file <file>``, to specify a file to inject at the REPL when "
"``Ctrl-K`` is pressed. This allows you to run a file (e.g. containing "
"some useful setup code, or even the program you are currently working "
"on)."
msgstr ""
"``--inject-file <file>``，指定按 ``Ctrl-K`` "
"时要在REPL中注入的文件。这允许你运行一个文件(例如，包含一些有用的设置代码，甚至是你目前正在处理的程序)。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:168
msgid ""
"While the ``repl`` command running, you can use ``Ctrl-]`` or ``Ctrl-x`` "
"to exit."
msgstr "在运行 ``repl`` 命令时，您可以使用 ``Ctrl-]`` 或 ``Ctrl-x`` 退出。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:171
msgid ""
"**Note:** The name \"REPL\" here reflects that the common usage of this "
"command to access the Read Eval Print Loop that is running on the "
"MicroPython device. Strictly, the ``repl`` command is just functioning as"
" a terminal (or \"serial monitor\") to access the device. Because this "
"command does not trigger the :ref:`auto-reset behavior <mpremote_reset>`,"
" this means that if a program is currently running, you will first need "
"to interrupt it with ``Ctrl-C`` to get to the REPL, which will then allow"
" you to access program state. You can also use ``mpremote soft-reset "
"repl`` to get a \"clean\" REPL with all program state cleared."
msgstr ""
"**注意:** 此处的名称 \"REPL\" 反映了该命令用于访问MicroPython设备上运行的Read Eval Print "
"Loop的常用用法。严格地说，``repl`` "
"命令只是作为终端(或“串行监视器”)来访问设备。因为这个命令不会触发:ref:`auto-reset behavior "
"<mpremote_reset>`，这意味着如果一个程序当前正在运行，您将首先需要用 ``Ctrl-C`` "
"中断它以进入REPL，这将允许您访问程序状态。您还可以使用 ``mpremote soft-reset repl`` 来获得清除所有程序状态的 "
"\"clean\" repl。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:183
msgid "**eval** -- evaluate and print the result of a Python expression:"
msgstr "**eval**-- 计算并打印Python表达式的结果:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:191
msgid "**exec** -- execute the given Python code:"
msgstr "**exec** -- 执行给定的Python代码:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:197
msgid ""
"By default, ``mpremote exec`` will display any output from the expression"
" until it terminates. The ``--no-follow`` flag can be specified to return"
" immediately and leave the device running the expression in the "
"background."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，``mpremote exec`` 将显示表达式的任何输出，直到它终止。可以指定 ``--no-follow`` "
"标志来立即返回，并让设备在后台运行表达式。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:203
msgid "**run** -- run a script from the local filesystem:"
msgstr "**run** -- 从本地文件系统运行脚本:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:209
msgid ""
"This will execute the file directly from RAM on the device without "
"copying it to the filesystem. This is a very useful way to iterate on the"
" development of a single piece of code without having to worry about "
"deploying it to the filesystem."
msgstr "这将直接从设备上的RAM执行文件，而不将其复制到文件系统中。这是一种非常有用的方法，可以迭代开发一段代码，而不必担心将其部署到文件系统中。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:214
msgid ""
"By default, ``mpremote run`` will display any output from the script "
"until it terminates. The ``--no-follow`` flag can be specified to return "
"immediately and leave the device running the script in the background."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下， ``mpremote run`` 将显示脚本的任何输出，直到脚本终止。可以指定 ``--no-follow`` "
"标志来立即返回并让设备在后台运行脚本。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:220
msgid "**fs** -- execute filesystem commands on the device:"
msgstr "**fs** -- 在设备上执行文件系统命令："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:226 ../../reference/mpremote.rst:387
msgid "``<sub-command>`` may be:"
msgstr "``<sub-command>`` 可以是："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:228
msgid "``cat <file..>`` to show the contents of a file or files on the device"
msgstr "``cat <file..>`` 显示设备上一个或多个文件的内容"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:229
msgid "``ls`` to list the current directory"
msgstr "``ls`` 列出当前目录"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:230
msgid "``ls <dirs...>`` to list the given directories"
msgstr "``ls <dirs...>`` 列出给定的目录"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:231
msgid "``cp [-rf] <src...> <dest>`` to copy files"
msgstr "``cp [-rf] <src...> <dest>`` 复制文件"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:232
msgid "``rm [-r] <src...>`` to remove files or folders on the device"
msgstr "``rm [-r] <src...>`` 删除设备上的文件或文件夹"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:233
msgid "``mkdir <dirs...>`` to create directories on the device"
msgstr "``mkdir <dirs...>`` 在设备上创建目录"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:234
msgid "``rmdir <dirs...>`` to remove directories on the device"
msgstr "``rmdir <dirs...>`` 删除设备上的目录"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:235
msgid "``touch <file..>`` to create the files (if they don't already exist)"
msgstr "``touch <file..>`` 创建文件（如果文件不存在）"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:236
msgid "``sha256sum <file..>`` to calculate the SHA256 sum of files"
msgstr "``sha256sum <file..>`` 计算文件的 SHA256 校验和"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:237
msgid "``tree [-vsh] <dirs...>`` to print a tree of the given directories"
msgstr "``tree [-vsh] <dirs...>`` 打印给定目录的树状结构"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:239
msgid ""
"The ``cp`` command uses a convention where a leading ``:`` represents a "
"remote path. Without a leading ``:`` means a local path. This is based on"
" the convention used by the `Secure Copy Protocol (scp) client "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secure_copy_protocol>`_."
msgstr ""
"``cp`` 命令使用一个约定，其中前导 ``:`` 表示远程路径。没有前导 ``:`` 表示本地路径。这是基于 `Secure Copy "
"Protocol (scp) client "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secure_copy_protocol>`_ 使用的约定。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:244
msgid ""
"So for example, ``mpremote fs cp main.py :main.py`` copies ``main.py`` "
"from the current local directory to the remote filesystem, whereas "
"``mpremote fs cp :main.py main.py`` copies ``main.py`` from the device "
"back to the current directory."
msgstr ""
"例如，``mpremote fs cp main.py :main.py`` 将 ``main.py`` 从当前本地目录复制到远程文件系统，而 "
"``mpremote fs cp :main.py main.py`` 将 ``main.py`` 从设备复制回当前目录。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:249
msgid ""
"The ``mpremote rm -r`` command accepts both relative and absolute paths. "
"Use ``:`` to refer to the current remote working directory (cwd) to allow"
" a directory tree to be removed from the device's default path (eg "
"``/flash``, ``/``). Use ``-v/--verbose`` to see the files being removed."
msgstr ""
"``mpremote rm -r`` 命令接受相对路径和绝对路径。"
"使用 ``:`` 引用当前远程工作目录（cwd），以便从设备的默认路径（如 ``/flash``、``/``）中删除目录树。"
"使用 ``-v/--verbose`` 查看正在删除的文件。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:254
msgid "For example:"
msgstr "例如："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:256
msgid ""
"``mpremote rm -r :libs`` will remove the ``libs`` directory and all its "
"child items from the device."
msgstr "``mpremote rm -r :libs`` 将从设备上删除 ``libs`` 目录及其所有子项。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:258
msgid ""
"``mpremote rm -rv :/sd`` will remove all files from a mounted SDCard and "
"result in a non-blocking warning. The mount will be retained."
msgstr "``mpremote rm -rv :/sd`` 将从已挂载的 SD 卡中删除所有文件，并产生一个非阻塞警告。挂载将被保留。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:260
msgid ""
"``mpremote rm -rv :/`` will remove all files on the device, including any"
" located in mounted vfs such as ``/sd`` or ``/flash``. After removing all"
" folders and files, this will  also return an error to mimic unix ``rm "
"-rf /`` behaviour."
msgstr ""
"``mpremote rm -rv :/`` 将删除设备上的所有文件，包括位于已挂载 vfs（如 ``/sd`` 或 ``/flash``）中的文件。"
"删除所有文件夹和文件后，还将返回错误以模仿 unix ``rm -rf /`` 的行为。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:265
msgid ""
"There is no supported way to undelete files removed by ``mpremote rm -r "
":``. Please use with caution."
msgstr "没有支持的方法来恢复被 ``mpremote rm -r :`` 删除的文件。请谨慎使用。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:268
msgid ""
"The ``tree`` command will print a tree of the given directories. Using "
"the ``--size/-s`` option will print the size of each file, or use "
"``--human/-h`` to use a more human readable format. Note: Directory size "
"is only printed when a non-zero size is reported by the device's "
"filesystem. The ``-v`` option  can be used to include the name of the "
"serial device in the output."
msgstr ""
"``tree`` 命令将打印给定目录的树状结构。使用 ``--size/-s`` 选项将打印每个文件的大小，"
"或使用 ``--human/-h`` 以更易读的格式显示。注意：仅当设备文件系统报告非零大小时才打印目录大小。"
"``-v`` 选项可用于在输出中包含串行设备的名称。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:275
msgid ""
"All other commands implicitly assume the path is a remote path, but the "
"``:`` can be optionally used for clarity."
msgstr "所有其他命令隐式假设路径为远程路径，但可以选择性地使用 ``:`` 以便更清晰。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:278
msgid ""
"All of the filesystem sub-commands take multiple path arguments, so if "
"there is another command in the sequence, you must use ``+`` to terminate"
" the arguments, e.g."
msgstr "所有的文件系统子命令都接受多个路径参数，所以如果序列中有另一个命令，您必须使用 ``+`` 来终止参数，例如。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:286
msgid ""
"This will copy the file to the device then enter the REPL. The ``+`` "
"prevents ``\"repl\"`` being interpreted as a path."
msgstr "这将把文件复制到设备上，然后输入REPL。``+`` 防止 ``\"repl\"`` 被解释为路径。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:289
msgid ""
"The ``cp`` command supports the ``-r`` option to make a recursive copy.  "
"By default ``cp`` will skip copying files to the remote device if the "
"SHA256 hash of the source and destination file matches.  To force a copy "
"regardless of the hash use the ``-f`` option."
msgstr ""
"``cp`` 命令支持 ``-r`` 选项以进行递归复制。默认情况下，如果源文件和目标文件的 SHA256 哈希值匹配，"
"``cp`` 将跳过向远程设备复制文件。要强制复制而不考虑哈希值，请使用 ``-f`` 选项。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:294
msgid ""
"**Note:** For convenience, all of the filesystem sub-commands are also "
":ref:`aliased as regular commands <mpremote_shortcuts>`, i.e. you can "
"write ``mpremote cp ...`` instead of ``mpremote fs cp ...``."
msgstr ""
"**注意:** 为了方便起见，所有的文件系统子命令也是:ref:`aliased as regular commands "
"<mpremote_shortcuts>`，即你可以写 ``mpremote cp ...`` 而不是 ``mpremote fs cp "
"...``。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:300
msgid "**df** -- query device free/used space"
msgstr "**df** -- 查询设备空闲/已用空间"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:306
msgid ""
"The ``df`` command will print size/used/free statistics for the device "
"filesystem, similar to the Unix ``df`` command."
msgstr "``df`` 命令将打印设备文件系统的大小/已使用/空闲统计信息，类似于Unix的 ``df`` 命令。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:311
msgid "**edit** -- edit a file on the device:"
msgstr "**edit** -- 编辑设备上的文件："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:317
msgid ""
"The ``edit`` command will copy each file from the device to a local "
"temporary directory and then launch your editor for each file (defined by"
" the environment variable ``$EDITOR``). If the editor exits successfully,"
" the updated file will be copied back to the device."
msgstr ""
"``edit`` 命令将每个文件从设备复制到本地临时目录，然后为每个文件启动编辑器(由环境变量 ``$EDITOR`` "
"定义)。如果编辑器成功退出，更新后的文件将被复制回设备。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:324
msgid ""
"**mip** -- install packages from :term:`micropython-lib` (or GitHub) "
"using the ``mip`` tool:"
msgstr "**mip** —— 使用 ``mip`` 工具从 :term:`micropython-lib` (或 GitHub)安装包:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:330
msgid "See :ref:`packages` for more information."
msgstr "参见 :ref:`packages` 了解更多信息。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:334
msgid "**mount** -- mount the local directory on the remote device:"
msgstr "**mount** -- 将本地目录挂载到远端设备上："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:340
msgid ""
"This allows the remote device to see the local host directory as if it "
"were its own filesystem. This is useful for development, and avoids the "
"need to copy files to the device while you are working on them."
msgstr "这允许远程设备查看本地主机目录，就好像它是自己的文件系统一样。这对开发很有用，并且避免了在处理文件时将文件复制到设备上的需要。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:344
msgid ""
"The device installs a filesystem driver, which is then mounted in the "
":ref:`device VFS <filesystem>` as ``/remote``, which uses the serial "
"connection to ``mpremote`` as a side-channel to access files. The device "
"will have its current working directory (via ``os.chdir``) set to "
"``/remote`` so that imports and file access will occur there instead of "
"the default filesystem path while the mount is active."
msgstr ""
"设备安装一个文件系统驱动程序，然后将其挂载在 :ref:`device VFS <filesystem>` 中作为 ``/remote``，它使用到"
" ``mpremote`` 的串行连接作为访问文件的侧通道。设备将把其当前工作目录(通过 ``os.chdir``)设置为 ``/remote``"
" ，以便在挂载活动时在那里进行导入和文件访问，而不是默认的文件系统路径。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:351
msgid ""
"**Note:** If the ``mount`` command is not followed by another action in "
"the sequence, a ``repl`` command will be implicitly added to the end of "
"the sequence."
msgstr "**注意:** 如果 ``mount`` 命令后面没有其他操作，那么 ``repl`` 命令将隐式地添加到序列的末尾。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:355
msgid ""
"During usage, Ctrl-D will trigger a soft-reset as normal, but the mount "
"will automatically be re-connected. If the unit has a main.py running at "
"startup however the remount cannot occur. In this case a raw mode soft "
"reboot can be used: Ctrl-A Ctrl-D to reboot, then Ctrl-B to get back to "
"normal repl at which point the mount will be ready."
msgstr ""
"在使用过程中， Ctrl-D "
"将像往常一样触发软复位，但是挂载将自动重新连接。如果单元在启动时运行main.py，但是无法进行重新加载。在这种情况下，可以使用原始模式软重启：按"
" Ctrl-A按 Ctrl-D 重新启动，然后按 Ctrl-B恢复到正常repl，此时装入将准备好。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:363
msgid ""
"``-l``, ``--unsafe-links``: By default an error will be raised if the "
"device accesses a file or directory which is outside (up one or more "
"directory levels) the local directory that is mounted.  This option "
"disables this check for symbolic links, allowing the device to follow "
"symbolic links outside of the local directory."
msgstr ""
"``-l``, ``--unsafe-links``: "
"默认情况下，如果设备访问的文件或目录位于挂载的本地目录之外(在一个或多个目录级别上)，将引发错误。该选项禁用对符号链接的检查，允许设备跟踪本地目录之外的符号链接。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:370
msgid "**unmount** -- unmount the local directory from the remote device:"
msgstr "**unmount**——从远端设备上卸载本地目录:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:376
msgid ""
"This happens automatically when ``mpremote`` terminates, but it can be "
"used in a sequence to unmount an earlier mount before subsequent command "
"are run."
msgstr "当 ``mpremote`` 终止时将自动发生，但它可以在序列中使用，以在运行后续命令之前卸载之前的挂载。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:381
msgid "**romfs** -- manage ROMFS partitions on the device:"
msgstr "**romfs** -- 管理设备上的 ROMFS 分区："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:389
msgid "``romfs query`` to list all the available ROMFS partitions and their size"
msgstr "``romfs query`` 列出所有可用的 ROMFS 分区及其大小"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:390
msgid ""
"``romfs [-o <output>] build <source>`` to create a ROMFS image from the "
"given source directory; the default output file is the source appended by"
" ``.romfs``"
msgstr ""
"``romfs [-o <output>] build <source>`` 从给定的源目录创建 ROMFS 镜像；"
"默认输出文件为源目录名加上 ``.romfs`` 后缀"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:392
msgid ""
"``romfs [-p <partition>] deploy <source>`` to deploy a ROMFS image to the"
" device; will also create a temporary ROMFS image if the source is a "
"directory"
msgstr ""
"``romfs [-p <partition>] deploy <source>`` 将 ROMFS 镜像部署到设备；"
"如果源是目录，还将创建临时 ROMFS 镜像"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:395
msgid ""
"The ``build`` and ``deploy`` sub-commands both support the "
"``-m``/``--mpy`` option to automatically compile ``.py`` files to "
"``.mpy`` when creating the ROMFS image. This option is enabled by "
"default, but only works if the ``mpy_cross`` Python package has been "
"installed (eg via ``pip install mpy_cross``).  If the package is not "
"installed then a warning is printed and ``.py`` files remain as is.  "
"Compiling of ``.py`` files can be disabled with the ``--no-mpy`` option."
msgstr ""
"``build`` 和 ``deploy`` 子命令都支持 ``-m``/``--mpy`` 选项，"
"在创建 ROMFS 镜像时自动将 ``.py`` 文件编译为 ``.mpy``。此选项默认启用，"
"但仅在安装了 ``mpy_cross`` Python 包（例如通过 ``pip install mpy_cross``）时有效。"
"如果未安装该包，则会打印警告且 ``.py`` 文件保持不变。"
"可以使用 ``--no-mpy`` 选项禁用 ``.py`` 文件的编译。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:404
msgid "**rtc** -- set/get the device clock (RTC):"
msgstr "**rtc** -- 设置/获取设备时钟（RTC）："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:410
msgid ""
"This will query the device RTC for the current time and print it as a "
"datetime tuple."
msgstr "这将查询设备RTC的当前时间，并将其打印为日期时间元组。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:417
msgid "This will set the device RTC to the host PC's current time."
msgstr "这将设置设备RTC为主机PC的当前时间。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:421
msgid "**sleep** -- sleep (delay) before executing the next command"
msgstr "**sleep** -- 在执行下一个命令之前休眠(延迟)"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:427
msgid ""
"This will pause execution of the command sequence for the specified "
"duration in seconds, e.g. to wait for the device to do something."
msgstr "这将暂停命令序列的执行，持续指定的秒数，例如等待设备执行某些操作。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:432
msgid "**reset** -- hard reset the device"
msgstr "**reset** -- 硬复位设备"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:438
msgid "**Note:** hard reset is equivalent to :func:`machine.reset`."
msgstr "**注:** 硬复位相当于 :func:`machine.reset`。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:442
msgid "**bootloader** enter the bootloader"
msgstr "**bootloader** 输入引导加载程序"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:448
msgid ""
"This will make the device enter its bootloader. The bootloader is port- "
"and board-specific (e.g. DFU on stm32, UF2 on rp2040/Pico)."
msgstr "这将使设备进入其引导加载程序。引导加载程序是特定于移植版本和主板的(例如stm32上的DFU, rp2040/Pico上的UF2)。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:454
msgid "Auto connection and soft-reset"
msgstr "自动连接和软复位"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:456
msgid ""
"Connection and disconnection will be done automatically at the start and "
"end of the execution of the tool, if such commands are not explicitly "
"given.  Automatic connection will search for the first available USB "
"serial device."
msgstr "如果没有明确给出这样的命令，将在工具执行的开始和结束时自动完成连接和断开连接。自动连接将搜索第一个可用的USB串行设备。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:460
msgid ""
"Once connected to a device, ``mpremote`` will automatically soft-reset "
"the device if needed.  This clears the Python heap and restarts the "
"interpreter, making sure that subsequent Python code executes in a fresh "
"environment.  Auto soft-reset is performed the first time one of the "
"following commands are executed: ``mount``, ``eval``, ``exec``, ``run``, "
"``fs``.  After doing a soft-reset for the first time, it will not be done"
" again automatically, until a ``disconnect`` command is issued."
msgstr ""
"一旦连接到设备，``mpremote`` "
"将自动软复位设备，如果需要的话。这将清除Python堆并重新启动解释器，确保后续Python代码在新的环境中执行。首次执行 ``mount`` 、"
" ``eval`` 、 ``exec`` 、 ``run`` 、 ``fs`` 等命令之一时，会自动软复位。第一次软复位后，在发出 "
"``disconnect`` 命令之前，不会自动重新复位。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:468
msgid ""
"Auto-soft-reset behaviour can be controlled by the ``resume`` command. "
"This might be useful to use the ``eval`` command to inspect the state of "
"of the device.  The ``soft-reset`` command can be used to perform an "
"explicit soft reset in the middle of a sequence of commands."
msgstr ""
"自动软复位行为可以通过 ``resume`` 命令控制。这可能是有用的使用 ``eval`` 命令检查设备的状态。``soft-reset`` "
"命令可用于在命令序列的中间执行显式软复位。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:476
msgid "Shortcuts"
msgstr "快捷键"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:478
msgid "Shortcuts can be defined using the macro system.  Built-in shortcuts are:"
msgstr "可以使用宏系统定义快捷方式。内置快捷方式有:"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:480
msgid "``devs``: Alias for ``connect list``"
msgstr "``devs``: `` 连接列表`` 的别称"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:482
msgid "``a0``, ``a1``, ``a2``, ``a3``: Aliases for ``connect /dev/ttyACMn``"
msgstr "``a0``, ``a1``, ``a2``, ``a3``: ``connect /dev/ttyACMn`` 的别称"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:484
msgid "``u0``, ``u1``, ``u2``, ``u3``: Aliases for ``connect /dev/ttyUSBn``"
msgstr "``u0``, ``u1``, ``u2``, ``u3``: ``connect /dev/ttyUSBn`` 的别称"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:486
msgid "``c0``, ``c1``, ``c2``, ``c3``: Aliases for ``connect COMn``"
msgstr "``c0``, ``c1``, ``c2``, ``c3``: ``connect COMn`` 的别称"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:488
msgid ""
"``cat``, ``edit``, ``ls``, ``cp``, ``rm``, ``mkdir``, ``rmdir``, "
"``touch``: Aliases for ``fs <sub-command>``"
msgstr ""
"``cat``, ``edit``, ``ls``, ``cp``, ``rm``, ``mkdir``, ``rmdir``, "
"``touch``: ``fs <sub-command>`` 的别称"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:490
msgid ""
"Additional shortcuts can be defined in the user configuration file "
"``mpremote/config.py``, located in the User Configuration Directory. The "
"correct location for each OS is determined using the ``platformdirs`` "
"module."
msgstr ""
"其他快捷方式可以在用户配置文件 ``mpremote/config.py`` 中定义，该文件位于用户配置目录中。"
"每个操作系统的正确位置使用 ``platformdirs`` 模块确定。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:494
msgid ""
"This is typically: - ``$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/mpremote/config.py`` - "
"``$HOME/.config/mpremote/config.py`` - "
"``$env:LOCALAPPDATA/mpremote/config.py``"
msgstr ""
"通常为：- ``$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/mpremote/config.py`` - "
"``$HOME/.config/mpremote/config.py`` - "
"``$env:LOCALAPPDATA/mpremote/config.py``"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:499
msgid ""
"The ``config.py``` file should define a dictionary named ``commands``. "
"The keys of this dictionary are the shortcuts and the values are either a"
" string or a list-of-strings:"
msgstr ""
"``config.py`` 文件应该定义一个名为 ``commands`` "
"的字典。这个字典的键是快捷方式，值是字符串或字符串列表："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:506
msgid "The command ``c33`` is replaced by ``connect id:334D335C3138``."
msgstr "命令 ``c33`` 替换为 ``connect id:334D335C3138``。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:512
msgid "The command ``test`` is replaced by ``mount . exec \"import test\"``."
msgstr "命令 ``test`` 已替换为 ``mount . exec \"import test\"``。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:514
msgid "Shortcuts can also accept arguments. For example:"
msgstr "快捷方式也可以接受参数。例如："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:520
msgid ""
"Running ``mpremote times 3 7`` will set ``x`` and ``y`` as variables on "
"the device, then evaluate the expression ``x*y``."
msgstr "运行 ``mpremote times 3 7`` 将设置 ``x`` 和 ``y`` 作为设备上的变量，然后计算表达式 ``x*y``。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:522
msgid "An example ``config.py`` might look like:"
msgstr "一个示例 ``config.py`` 文件可能如下所示："

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:548
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:554
msgid ""
"Connect to the first available device and implicitly run the ``repl`` "
"command."
msgstr "连接到第一个可用的设备并隐式运行 ``repl`` 命令。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:560
msgid ""
"Connect to the device at ``/dev/ttyACM1`` (Linux) and implicitly run the "
"``repl`` command. See :ref:`shortcuts <mpremote_shortcuts>` above."
msgstr ""
"连接到设备 ``/dev/ttyACM1`` (Linux) 并隐式运行 ``repl`` 命令。参阅上面的 :ref:`shortcuts "
"<mpremote_shortcuts>` 。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:567
msgid ""
"Connect to the device at ``COM1`` (Windows) and implicitly run the "
"``repl`` command. See :ref:`shortcuts <mpremote_shortcuts>` above."
msgstr ""
"在 ``COM1`` 连接到设备(Windows)并隐式运行 ``repl`` 命令。参阅上面的 :ref:`shortcuts "
"<mpremote_shortcuts>`。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:574
msgid ""
"Explicitly specify which device to connect to, and as above, implicitly "
"run the ``repl`` command."
msgstr "显式指定要连接到哪个设备，并像上面一样隐式运行 ``repl`` 命令。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:581
msgid "Connect to the device at ``/dev/ttyACM0`` and then run the ``ls`` command."
msgstr "在 ``/dev/ttyACM0`` 处连接到设备，然后运行 ``ls`` 命令。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:583
msgid "It is equivalent to ``mpremote connect /dev/ttyACM1 fs ls``."
msgstr "它相当于 ``mpremote connect /dev/ttyACM1 fs ls``。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:589
msgid ""
"Run the specified Python command and display any output. This is "
"equivalent to typing the command at the REPL prompt."
msgstr "运行指定的Python命令并显示输出结果。这相当于在REPL提示符下输入命令。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:596
msgid "Evaluate each expression in turn and print the results."
msgstr "依次计算每个表达式并打印结果。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:602
msgid ""
"Evaluate ``1/2`` on the device at ``/dev/ttyACM0``, then ``3/4`` on the "
"device at ``/dev/ttyACM1``, printing each result."
msgstr ""
"在位于 ``/dev/ttyACM0`` 的设备上计算 ``1/2`` ，然后在位于 ``/dev/ttyACM1`` 的设备上计算 "
"``3/4`` ，打印每个结果。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:609
msgid ""
"Connect to the device without triggering a :ref:`soft reset <soft_reset>`"
" and execute the ``print_state_info()`` function (e.g. to find out "
"information about the current program state), then trigger a soft reset."
msgstr ""
"在不触发 :ref:`soft reset <soft_reset>` 的情况下连接设备，并执行 "
"``print_state_info()`` 函数(例如，查找有关当前程序状态的信息)，然后触发软复位。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:617
msgid ""
"Hard-reset the device, wait 500ms for it to become available, then enter "
"the bootloader."
msgstr "硬复位设备，等待500毫秒使其可用，然后进入引导加载程序。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:624
msgid ""
"Update the copy of utils/driver.py on the device, then execute the local "
"``test.py`` script on the device. ``test.py`` is never copied to the "
"device filesystem, rather it is run from RAM."
msgstr ""
"更新设备上的utils/driver.py副本，然后在设备上执行本地 ``test.py`` 脚本。 ``test.py`` "
"永远不会复制到设备文件系统，而是从RAM运行。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:632
msgid ""
"Update the copy of utils/driver.py on the device, then execute app.py on "
"the device."
msgstr "更新设备上utils/driver.py的副本，然后在设备上执行app.py。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:635
msgid ""
"This is a common development workflow to update a single file and then "
"re-start your program. In this scenario, your ``main.py`` on the device "
"would also do ``import app``."
msgstr "这是更新单个文件然后重新启动程序的常见开发工作流。在这种情况下，设备上的 ``main.py`` 也会执行 ``import app``。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:643
msgid ""
"Update the copy of utils/driver.py on the device, then trigger a soft-"
"reset to restart your program, and then monitor the output via the "
"``repl`` command."
msgstr "更新设备上的utils/driver.py副本，然后触发软重置以重新启动程序，然后通过 ``repl`` 命令监视输出。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:650
msgid "Same as above, but update the entire utils directory first."
msgstr "与上面相同，但首先更新整个utils目录。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:656
msgid ""
"Mount the current local directory at ``/remote`` on the device and starts"
" a ``repl`` session which will use ``/remote`` as the working directory."
msgstr "将当前本地目录挂载到设备上的 ``/remote`` ，并启动 ``repl`` 会话，该会话将使用 ``/remote`` 作为工作目录。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:663
msgid ""
"After mounting the current local directory, executes ``demo.py`` from the"
" mounted directory."
msgstr "挂载当前本地目录后，从挂载的目录执行 ``demo.py`` 。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:670
msgid ""
"After mounting the local directory ``app`` as ``/remote`` on the device, "
"executes the local ``test.py`` from the host's current directory without "
"copying it to the filesystem."
msgstr ""
"在设备上将本地目录 ``app`` 挂载为 ``/remote`` 后，从主机的当前目录执行本地 ``test.py`` "
"，而不将其复制到文件系统中。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:678
msgid ""
"After mounting the current local directory, executes ``demo.py`` from the"
" mounted directory each time ``Ctrl-J`` is pressed."
msgstr "挂载当前本地目录后，每次按 ``Ctrl-J`` 时，从挂载的目录执行 ``demo.py`` 。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:681
msgid ""
"You will first need to press ``Ctrl-D`` to reset the interpreter state "
"(which will preserve the mount) before pressing ``Ctrl-J`` to re-import "
"``demo.py``."
msgstr "在按 ``Ctrl-J`` 重新导入 ``demo.py`` 之前，您首先需要按 ``Ctrl-D`` 重置解释器状态(这将保留挂载)。"

#: ../../reference/mpremote.rst:689
msgid ""
"Same as above, but executes the contents of the local file demo.py at the"
" REPL every time ``Ctrl-K`` is pressed. As above, use Ctrl-D to reset the"
" interpreter state first."
